Story: User wants to search for local water fountain 
  1. Request User Location
    - Good Path: user location access granted 
      Search for fountains based on user location
    - Bad path: user location access denied
      Ask user to select / input their location
  2. Display Map of local area with pins for each water fountain / building with a water fountain, filter about location from above
  3. User will either click on pin to see the building map for each level or once the user is within the boundary of a building
  4. Once the User is in or clicks a building, we show the bottom floor map with pins for each water fountain and then display buttons for each floor 
